casebody.data:
Askari Abdullah MUHAMMAD, fka Thomas Knight, petitioner,
v.
Michael D. CREWS, Secretary, Florida Department of Corrections, et al. No. 13-8154, 13A711. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 7, 2014.

Case below, 739 F.3d 683.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari *895to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
